<headline>Special Weather Statement issued April 22 at 5:15AM MDT  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Isolated Intense Snow Showers Over the Next Two Hours...
Surface observations and satellite imagery show isolated intense
snow showers in the Dillon area this morning reducing visibility
to below a half mile at times. A quick accumulation of up to an
inch will be possible with intense snow showers through 7 AM.
Expect rapid changes to visibility in any snow showers.</description>
